<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491733>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov. A–B. Habitus. Scale bars: 500 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491735>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov. A. Apex of Ant. IV (left side). B. Distal part of Ant. III (lateral side). C. Distal part of Ant. II (left side). D. Lateral process of labial palp (right side). E. Maxillary outer lobe (left side). F. Labial and mental chaetotaxy (right side). G. Labial palp and labium (right side). Scale bars: 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491735/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491737>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov. A. Labrum. B. Dorsal chaetotaxy of head (right side). C. Anterior part of dorsal head. D. Dorsal chaetotaxy of head (right side). Scale bars: 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491737/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491739>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov. A. Chaetotaxy of Th. II−III (right side). B. Trochanteral organ. C. Hind foot complex (anterior view). Scale bars: 30 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491739/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491741>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov., dorsal chaetotaxy (right side). A−B. Abd. I. C−D. Abd. II. Scale bars: 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491741/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491743>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov., dorsal chaetotaxy (right side). A. Abd. III. B. Lateral part of Abd. III. Scale bars: 30 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491743/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491745>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov., dorsal chaetotaxy (right side). A. Abd. IV. B. Anterior bothriotrichal complex of Abd. IV. Scale bars: 30 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491745/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491749>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov. A–B. Chaetotaxy of Abd. V (right side). C. Anterior face of ventral tube (right side). D. Posterior face of ventral tube (apically). E. Lateral flap of ventral tube. Scale bars: A−B = 15 μm; C−E = 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491749/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491751>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Lepidocyrtus (A.) huizhouensis sp. nov. A. Distal part of ventral manubrium (right side). B–C. Manubrial plaque and proximal part of dens (lateral view). D–E. Distal part of dens and mucro (lateral view). Scale bars: 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491751/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

